'''Lorenzo Lauria''' is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Bermuda Bowl]] (2) 2005, 2013 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Rosenblum Cup]] (2) 1998, 2002 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-open-teams.aspx Rosenblum Cup Winners]</ref>

* [[World Team Olympiad|World Olympiad Teams Championship]] (3) 2000, 2004, 2008

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (12)
